definitions.definition: An outer suburb of Bristol , England ; a southern district between Whitchurch , Brislington and Keynsham ( OS grid ref ST6268 ) .
A small village and civil parish (served by Chetnole and Stockwood Parish Council) in Dorset , England ( OS grid ref ST5807 ) .
